---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import AdSlot from "../components/AdSlot.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Mechascopic" description="About Mechascopic: games, guides, and creator updates.">
  <main>
    <h1>About Mechascopic</h1>
    <p>Ahoy, I'm Mechascopic, a gamer who loves playing all kinds of games and sharing that love with my kiddo.</p>
    <p>I've been gaming for as long as I can remember, and I've always enjoyed connecting with other players who love learning, improving, and having fun together.</p>
    <p>This channel is where I share my best gaming content, from calm PvE strategy and builds to live streams, gameplay videos, and occasional reviews.</p>
    <p>You'll find a strong focus on approachable Destiny 2 PvE guides, practical loadout ideas, and creator workflows that help players improve consistently.</p>
    <p>Whether you enjoy first-person shooters, indie games, or something in between, you'll find something here. I stream and post new videos regularly on YouTube.</p>
    <p>Come join the journey, hang out, learn new approaches, and have some fun.</p>
    <AdSlot label="About, mid page" minHeight="120px" />

    <section class="platforms" aria-label="Where to watch">
      <h2>Where to Watch</h2>
      <p class="platforms-intro">Everything is on YouTube right now: live streams, guide videos, and gameplay uploads.</p>

      <div class="platform-grid">
        <article class="platform-card">
          <h3>YouTube</h3>
          <p>Live streams, guide videos, build walkthroughs, and focused PvE tips you can revisit anytime.</p>
          <a href="https://youtube.com/@mechascopic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Watch on YouTube</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .platforms {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
  }

  .platforms-intro {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .platform-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }

  .platform-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 0.9rem;
  }

  .platform-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }

  .platform-card p {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
  }

  .platform-card a,
  .platform-card a:visited {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
    text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
  }

  .platform-card a:hover,
  .platform-card a:focus {
    color: var(--color-link-hover);
  }
</style>